25 November 2019 The Justice, Crime Prevention and Security (JCPS) Cluster Ministers will hold a media briefing to update the public on its successes and the plans for the festive season safety campaign. The details of the media briefing are as follows: Date: Tuesday, 26 November 2019Time: 14h00Venue: Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Parliament in Cape Town NB: There will be a video link to Ronnie Mamoepa Media Centre, Tshedimosetso House, Cnr Frances Baard and Festival streets, Hatfield in Pretoria. RSVPs:Pheliswa SebatiCell: 082 413 4609E-mail: pheliswa@gcis.gov.za Enquiries:Siphiwe DlaminiCell: 083 645 4294